SEO_TITLE: Kelvin Maina Wangari - Software Developer & IT Consultant
SEO_DESCRIPTION: A results-oriented Software Developer and IT Consultant with over five years of experience in full-lifecycle software development, including mobile and web applications. Proven ability to deliver high-quality solutions, from concept to deployment, for a diverse clientele. A dedicated and fast learner, committed to leveraging emerging technologies to solve complex problems and drive user engagement.
